{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-0000-4000-8000-quizlakecoll",
    "name": "QuizLake API",
    "description": "Коллекция для проверки всех эндпоинтов бэкенда QuizLake. Переменные (токены, id квиза/вопроса/сессии, код комнаты, id участников, id правильного варианта) сохраняются автоматически через тест-скрипты после успешных запросов, вручную копировать ничего не нужно.\n\nПорядок прогона (коллекцию можно гонять Runner'ом строго сверху вниз, без пропусков):\nAuth (Register -> Login) -> Categories -> Users -> Quizzes (Create -> Update quiz: set status ready) -> Questions (Create -> Get -> Update) -> Quiz Sessions (Create -> Get discover feed -> Get by code -> Join -> Get participants -> Next question) -> Participant Answers (Submit answer -> Reveal answer -> End game) -> Leave & Cancel session (отдельная вторая сессия, не пересекается с основным потоком) -> WebSocket (см. описание папки, тестируется вручную в отдельной вкладке Postman) -> Cleanup (Delete question -> Delete quiz).\n\nПеред первым прогоном примени миграции (`alembic upgrade head`) — без них список категорий будет пустым, а на квизе останется лишнее поле points_per_correct.\n\nDelete quiz / Delete question вынесены в отдельную папку Cleanup в самом конце коллекции — все остальные папки (Questions, Quiz Sessions, Participant Answers, Leave & Cancel session) используют один и тот же quiz_id, поэтому удалять его раньше нельзя.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{access_token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:8000/api/v1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "ws_url", "value": "ws://localhost:8000/api/v1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "access_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "refresh_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "quiz_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "question_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "correct_option_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "session_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "room_code", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "participant_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "session_id_2", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "room_code_2", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "participant_id_2", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"first_name\": \"Test\",\n  \"last_name\": \"User\",\n  \"nickname\": \"testuser1\",\n  \"email\": \"test1@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"secret123\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set(\"access_token\", data.access_token);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set(\"refresh_token\", data.refresh_token);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"test1@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"secret123\",\n  \"remember_me\": true\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set(\"access_token\", data.access_token);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set(\"refresh_token\", data.refresh_token);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refresh_token\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/refresh",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "refresh"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refresh_token\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/logout",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "logout"]
            },
            "description": "Не запускать в середине потока — обнулит refresh_token, а он нужен дальше не будет (access_token из Login продолжит работать до истечения). Оставлено на самый конец."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Categories",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get categories",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/categories",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["categories"]
            },
            "description": "Должно вернуть 7 сидовых категорий (История, География, Наука и т.д.) — они добавляются миграцией `6f2a9d4b8c31_seed_default_categories`. Если список пустой — примени `alembic upgrade head`."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Users",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get me",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/me",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["users", "me"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update me",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"first_name\": \"Test (обновлено)\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/me",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["users", "me"]
            },
            "description": "Можно так же прислать nickname/email/avatar_url/password — все поля необязательные (exclude_unset)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get my stats",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/me/stats",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["users", "me", "stats"]
            },
            "description": "played/wins/avg_score_percent будут нулевыми, пока не пройдёшь Participant Answers -> End game хотя бы один раз (учитываются только finished-сессии)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get participation history",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/me/participation-history",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["users", "me", "participation-history"]
            },
            "description": "Пусто, пока текущий пользователь не сыграл (не был участником) ни в одной finished-сессии."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get hosted history",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/users/me/hosted-history",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["users", "me", "hosted-history"]
            },
            "description": "Появится запись после Participant Answers -> End game — там текущий пользователь выступает хостом."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Quizzes",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create quiz",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set(\"quiz_id\", data.id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Тестовый квиз\",\n  \"description\": \"Проверка эндпоинтов\",\n  \"is_public\": true\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/quizzes",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["quizzes"]
            },
            "description": "is_public: true — нужно, чтобы созданная позже сессия появилась в Discover-ленте (Quiz Sessions -> Get discover feed)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get my quizzes",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/quizzes?status=draft",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["quizzes"],
              "query": [{ "key": "status", "value": "draft", "disabled": true }]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get quiz by id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/quizzes/{{quiz_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["quizzes", "{{quiz_id}}"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update quiz (set status ready)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"ready\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/quizzes/{{quiz_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["quizzes", "{{quiz_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "ВАЖНО: выполнить перед созданием сессии (и обязательно после создания вопросов) — сессию нельзя запустить, пока квиз в статусе draft."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Questions",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create question",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set(\"question_id\", data.id);",
                  "const correct = data.answer_options.find((o) => o.is_correct);",
                  "if (correct) pm.collectionVariables.set(\"correct_option_id\", correct.id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"question_text\": \"Столица Франции?\",\n  \"question_type\": \"single\",\n  \"order_index\": 1,\n  \"time_limit_sec\": 15,\n  \"points\": 100,\n  \"answer_options\": [\n    { \"option_text\": \"Париж\", \"is_correct\": true, \"order_index\": 1 },\n    { \"option_text\": \"Лондон\", \"is_correct\": false, \"order_index\": 2 },\n    { \"option_text\": \"Берлин\", \"is_correct\": false, \"order_index\": 3 }\n  ]\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/quizzes/{{quiz_id}}/questions",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["quizzes", "{{quiz_id}}", "questions"]
            },
            "description": "Тест-скрипт заодно сохраняет correct_option_id (id варианта «Париж») — он нужен дальше для Participant Answers -> Submit answer."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get questions",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/quizzes/{{quiz_id}}/questions",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["quizzes", "{{quiz_id}}", "questions"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update question",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"question_text\": \"Столица Франции (обновлено)?\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/quizzes/{{quiz_id}}/questions/{{question_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["quizzes", "{{quiz_id}}", "questions", "{{question_id}}"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
